					[ [ 'After the {{subject}} look specifically? This is where {{site_name}} files it — {{primary_keyword}} groups every matching performer and clip so the page opens already focused.', 'Here for the {{subject}} look and nothing else? {{primary_keyword}} has gathered it on {{site_name}}, so you begin from the appearance instead of filtering your way toward it.' ], [ 'A shared look tells you what to expect at a glance and almost nothing about the rest, which is why the individual pages carry so much of what actually separates them.' ], [ 'One pass through {{kw1}} and the real range inside this look starts to show.', 'One pass through the set and the real range inside this look starts to show.' ], '{{intent_clarity_1}}' ],
