					[ [ 'A page can run thin on words and still open onto something complete, so hold your judgement until you have looked.', 'Sparse copy and a strong session go together more often than you would expect, which is why a quick look beats an early no.' ], 'Where the writing is light, the thumbnail and the destination page usually carry what it leaves unsaid.', [ 'Anchor on the fuller listings, but let {{kw1}} make its case before you rule it out.', 'Anchor on the fuller listings, but let the quiet ones make their case before you rule them out.' ], '{{intent_clarity_3}}' ],
					[ [ 'The length of a listing is a poor guide to what is behind it, so give the short ones a fair hearing.', 'Short does not mean lesser here; a spare page can lead somewhere well worth the click.' ], 'A quiet write-up usually says more about how the performer approaches their page than about the session itself.', [ 'Lean on the detailed pages first, then check {{kw1}} rather than skipping straight past it.', 'Lean on the detailed pages first, then check the sparse ones rather than skipping straight past them.' ], '{{intent_clarity_3}}' ],
					[ [ 'Read a thin listing as an opening question, not a closed one — the images and the room often answer what the text does not.', 'A brief page leaves gaps on purpose or by habit, and those gaps are usually filled once you follow it through.' ], 'How much a performer writes is a style choice, so the sparse pages deserve the same second glance as the full ones.', [ 'Let the fuller pages lead and still give {{kw1}} a look before it drops off your list.', 'Let the fuller pages lead and still give the quiet ones a look before they drop off your list.' ], '{{intent_clarity_3}}' ],
					[ [ 'A spare page can hide a strong session, so treat light wording as a prompt to look rather than a signal to skip.', 'Thin copy is an invitation to check, not a reason to pass, since the substance often sits in the images or the room.' ], 'The write-up reflects the performer\'s habits far more than the experience waiting behind the link.', [ 'Shortlist from the detailed pages, but open {{kw1}} before you decide against it.', 'Shortlist from the detailed pages, but open the sparse ones before you decide against them.' ], '{{intent_clarity_3}}' ],
